sequenceDiagram
    participant ES as ExecutionService
    participant HS as HistoryService
    participant HR as HistoryRepository
    participant MB as MessageBroker

    ES->>ES: フロー実行完了
    ES->>ES: ExecutionRecord 構築<br>(全ノード結果を集約)
    ES->>HS: saveRecord(record)
    HS->>HS: cleanupOldRecords(flowId)
    HS->>HR: count(flowId)
    HR-->>HS: 現在の履歴件数

    alt 保持件数超過
        HS->>HR: list(flowId)
        HR-->>HS: 履歴一覧(日時順)
        HS->>HR: delete(最古レコードID)
    end

    HS->>HR: save(record)
    HR-->>HS: 保存完了
    HS-->>ES: 保存完了

    ES->>MB: execution:flowCompleted
    MB->>MB: VSCode 通知表示<br>(成功/失敗)
